One of the most successful live acts on the road today, Elton and his band put on an unforgettable show: the entire audience standing, dancing and singing along with much-loved classic songs.Learn MoreCéline Dion
One of the most immediately recognized, widely respected and successful performers in pop music history, Céline Dion returns to The Colosseum at Caesars Palace.Learn MoreAbsinthe
