Five-time Grammy® Award winner CeeLo Green will perform an intimate four-night limited engagement at the iconic Cleopatra’s Barge at Caesars Palace from July 21 – 29.Buy TicketsThe Who
One of rock’s most legendary and defining bands, THE WHO, joins the home of the greatest entertainers in the world as the first rock band to take residency at The Colosseum since the venue opened in 2003. The first run of six shows is scheduled July 29 through August 11 and $1 from each ticket sold will benefit Teen Cancer America.Learn More








