CORPORATE ENTERTAINMENT 
        FOR EVENTS NATIONWIDE
      Tim Decker will bring his high energy, fast-paced speed painting performance 
      to your next corporate event. Engage your crowd with this unique, exciting 
      corporate entertainment. 

      The show is customizable and can include a painting to deliver a message 
      or incorporate your brand along with the entertainment. Hold an extraordinary 
      corporate event and make your message memorable. 
      Performance is Perfect for: 
      
Corporate Awards Dinners 
Corporate Holiday Parties and Events
Client Events
Conference Entertainment
Product Launches 
Employee/Customer Appreciation Events
Opening and Closing Sessions for Meetings and Training Programs
Any corporate event you want to inspire, engage, and impress


 
