 CUSTOMIZED SHOW TIME

        On a tight schedule but want to make your company event memorable? Tim 
        can custom tailor a show just for your corporate event. He is extremely 
        easy to work with. Tell him your time frame and he does the rest. 
 CUSTOM CEO/GUEST 
        SPEAKER INTRODUCTIONS

        Want a unique way to introduce your CEO, Guest Speaker, or a special guest 
        at your corporate event? Have Tim introduce them by painting them live 
        in under 5 minutes. Talk about memorable. 
 BE THE HERO

        Dont risk the wrong corporate entertainment. Book Tim and sit back, relax, 
        and take all the credit. Your guests will compliment and thank you and 
        your boss will give you a raise. (I cant guarantee the raise but would 
        like to think you will get one for your great decision.) 





  
 
  



